quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  12,64,"O maaki: \"Hara mi hooloray on e fii makko, si wanaa no mi hoolornoo on non e neene-gooto makko on ko adii? Ko Alla woni mo∆ī∆īo reenoowo, ko Kanko …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude yurmetee…ďe …ďen"
  12,65,"Nde …ďe udditunoo doŇčlle ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe tawi coggeeli(njigguuji) ma…ď…ďe …óin ruttaama e ma…ď…ďe. ∆Āe wi'i: \"Ko an yo ben amen, ko men …óa…ď…ďata [kadi]? ∆äii ko coggeeli amen, …ói ruttaama e amen. Me…óen jiggana yim…ďe amen, men reena musi…ó…óo amen on, men …ďeydora …ďetu ngelooba; …óum ko …ďetu newiingu"
  12,66,"O maaki: \"Mi immindintaa(neldatah) mo e moo…óon haa ∆īettanon mi ahadi ka Alla, wonnde on artiranay lam mo si wanaa hara on hu…ďinda\". ∆Āaawo …ďe ∆īettanii mo ahadi ma…ď…ďe ndin, o maaki: \"Alla e dow ko wowlu…óen kon, ko O deeno"
  12,67,"O maaki: \"Ko onon yo …ďi…ó…ďe am, wata on naatiroy e damal gootal, naatiree e dame seertu…óe. Mi dun-cantaa on e (muy…óe) Alla hay e huunde. √Ďaawoore alanaa si wanaa Alla: Ko e Makko mi fawii, ko e makko kadi, yo fawo fawotoo…ďe …ďen"
  12,68,"Nde …ďe naatirnoo nokku ka ben ma…ď…ďe yamirnoo …ďe …óon, …óum wonaano no duncana …ďe [ko iwri] ka Alla si wanaa haaju wonunoo…óo e fittaandu Yaaquuba mo o gasini. Kanko on, ko o jom-ganndal ngal Men anndini mo. Kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen …ďe anndaa"
  12,69,"Nde …ďe naatunoo ka Yuusufa, o ma…ď…ďi neene-gooto makko on e makko, o maaki: \"Ko mi neene-gooto maa, wata a sunor ko …ďe huuwaynoo"
